text: René G. J. Dercksen (born 11 December 1962) is a Dutch politician who has been a member of the Senate for the Party for Freedom from 9 June 2015 to 11 June 2019. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Senate (Netherlands) Category:Party for Freedom politicians Category:21st-century Dutch politicians Category:People from Rotterdam
